0557   0243             ; THING IN THE SAVE AREA (THIS IS INDICATED BY A NON-ZERO
0558   0243             ; 'LOPVAR'), THEN THE OLD SAVE AREA IS SAVED IN THE STACK
0559   0243             ; BEFORE THE NEW ONE OVERWRITES IT.
